      <originalsloc id="aspace_2c9ab29d0630d27859ec7a936558ff41">
         <head>Existence and Location of Originals</head>
         <p>The entire collection is available on microfilm (HM 263) and in the Thomas Heazle Parke Papers (MS 1643).   The papers consist of letters written by Thomas H. Parke to his sister, Isabel Beatty, about his travels with Henry M. Stanley in Africa. Also included are telegrams and newspapers clippings.</p>  
